</div>
<p local-id=3D"73ee52ec9bbf">For bullets 1 &amp; 2, the primary resolver is=
 PostgreSQL. ClickHouse is involved only when queries ask for run history o=
r flakiness trends.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"b1112468e05a" id=3D"TestHarness-DesignSpecification(Fullvis=
ion)-4.2ResponseShape">4.2 Response Shape</h3>
<p local-id=3D"9046743bfe6d">When an agent traverses to <code>-&gt; tests()=
</code>, it needs three things: what tests exist around the artefact, how w=
ell it's covered (and specifically where the gaps are), and a quick-read su=
mmary signal to guide its planning.</p>
<p local-id=3D"fbf76aeb0a01"><strong>Proposed logical response shape:</stro=
ng></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  artefact: {
    id,
    name,
    kind,
    file_path,
    span_start,
    span_end
  },

  covering_tests: [
    {
      test_id,
      test_name,
      suite_name,
      file_path,
      classification: unit | integration | e2e,
      classification_source: coverage_derived | convention,
      confidence: 0.0=E2=80=931.0,
      strength: 0.0=E2=80=931.0,
      last_run: {
        status: pass | fail | skip,
        duration_ms,
        commit_sha
      }
    }
  ],

  coverage: {
    line_coverage_pct,
    branch_coverage_pct,
    branches: [
      {
        location: { line, column, span },
        description,
        covered: bool,
        covering_test_ids: []
      }
    ]
  },

  summary: {
    verification_level: well_tested | partially_tested | untested,
    total_covering_tests,
    unit_count,
    integration_count,
    e2e_count,
    untested_branch_count
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"64c0aa4c1814"><strong>Field notes:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"2cba0d30-cc39-421a-b950-593ad127ecc8">
<li local-id=3D"91e74772-7d0e-4293-a675-fc0900d9b2c3">
<p local-id=3D"ad4569b63ea7"><code>covering_tests.confidence</code> =E2=80=
=94 Linkage quality: how sure are we this test actually touches this artefa=
ct? Coverage-verified execution gets high confidence. Static-only linkage (=
import/reference detected but no execution confirmation) gets lower confide=
nce.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ecd222f-65a7-436e-bc30-d175efd4cfaa">
<p local-id=3D"74cdecb3dd59"><code>covering_tests.strength</code> =E2=80=94=
 Verification value: how much does this test actually prove about this arte=
fact? A focused unit test directly targeting the artefact scores high. An e=
2e test passing through incidentally among many artefacts scores low. Deriv=
ed from test classification and fan-out.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"09b80fbc-c758-4f92-b8e7-e093ee92300d">
<p local-id=3D"68f60d02b3cd"><code>covering_tests.last_run</code> =E2=80=94=
 The agent needs to know if a test is currently passing or failing before m=
aking changes. A pre-existing failure is very different from one the agent =
introduces.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db1ca9ad-126a-4d66-b7e1-682c42d92867">
<p local-id=3D"5fcde8be7ff4"><code>coverage.branches</code> =E2=80=94 Lists=
 every branch individually with a covered/not-covered flag. Rather than jus=
t "72% branch coverage," the agent can see exactly which branches are untes=
ted and reason about whether its change affects those paths.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9962b3ef-d873-4edb-8529-7b9df58afe53">
<p local-id=3D"28c5ea37b307"><code>summary.verification_level</code> =E2=80=
=94 Quick-read signal. An agent can use this to decide upfront whether it n=
eeds to write new tests as part of its task.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8d38175-1782-473a-88e9-7339594955dc">
<p local-id=3D"8a95cfeb4b40"><code>commit_sha</code> =E2=80=94 Not surfaced=
 in the top-level response. The query resolves against a specific commit vi=
a <code>asOf()</code> in the DevQL pipeline and all returned data is from t=
hat snapshot. Traceability is maintained internally.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"2671b375962f" id=3D"TestHarness-DesignSpecification(Fullvis=
ion)-4.3OpenDesignQuestions">4.3 Open Design Questions</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"52=
e68423-af9c-411b-a14b-4b9d0b678a48" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"dd3de937-eaa8-4b1c-9009-36301499b7d8">
<th data-local-id=3D"7a3c8b67-2337-47d1-bd72-c69ca07e3c27" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6319960ab4b6">ID</p></th>
