<p local-id=3D"2fe512b98145"><strong>Qodo-Embed-1-1.5B</strong> is the curr=
ent standout for local deployment. It surpasses much larger models on the C=
oIR benchmark (the industry standard for code retrieval), including OpenAI'=
s text-embedding-3-large (65.17). Built on Qwen2 and trained with a synthet=
ic data pipeline that generates natural language descriptions for code. Exp=
licitly supports TypeScript.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9daa139d9033"><strong>Nomic CodeRankEmbed-137M</strong> is n=
otable as an ultra-lightweight option at ~521MB. It can run on CPU, making =
it viable on any developer machine. Could serve as a fast first-pass retrie=
ver, paired with a larger model for reranking.</p>
<p local-id=3D"bb8db33df27c"><strong>Nomic Embed Code (7B)</strong> achieve=
s state-of-the-art on CodeSearchNet but at ~26GB is heavy for local deploym=
ent. Better suited for Enterprise Edition or server-side use.</p>
